column5: In case anyone is interested I will have the auction list on May 5th. Can't give it out before then as once it's listed it can't be sold if someone comes along tomorrow wanting to buy it retail.  Temagami Marine is auctioning off some used boats, some NEW older non current boats (This may include a 2006 Lund 20' Pro Angler.. not sure yet), used outboard motors, 2 forklifts, new ATV's and some "parts boats and engines" that are laying around.
did i miss something?  are they shutting there doors?
NO !!!!! Just what it says.. used boats... old stock etc.  Marina is just fine.
Your's isn't on the block is it?
LOL Roy... I'm just ticked that I have to be in Ottawa on the 9th for a wedding so can't be there to bid.
It would be greatly appreciated if you would post a link to the list once you get it.

Okay... so here's the list. There may be some more additions of project boats and misc before Saturday. Note that many of these 2006 boats/packages are brand new. They have Registration marks already to facilitate an easy change of ownership. Gonna be some BIG deals in there...and I'm am waiting for confirmation if there are any reserves. I was correct as well... the 2006 Lund 2000 Pro Angler is an item and it's a BEAUTY for anyone that likes downrigging the great lakes especially. Picture of it attached below from fall 2006. It's prerigged for Mercs.. main and kicker.
